---
<section class="py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Verde glow de fondo -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
    style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(26,225,122,0.07), transparent)"
  ></div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center relative z-10 reveal">

    <!-- Precio grande -->
    <div class="inline-flex items-baseline gap-4 mb-6">
      <span
        class="font-display font-extrabold text-gradient"
        style="font-size: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 8rem); line-height: 1"
      >
        $3,000
      </span>
      <span class="text-muted text-2xl font-semibold">MXN</span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="font-display font-bold tracking-tight mb-4" style="font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.5rem)">
      Lo pagas una vez y ya quedó.
    </h2>

    <p class="text-muted text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-3">
      No hay mensualidades. No hay renovaciones. No hay letra chica.
      Mientras la competencia te cobra cada mes, tú ya terminaste de pagar.
    </p>

    <!-- Comparativa rápida en línea -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-10 text-sm">
      <span class="text-muted/60 line-through">Microsip: pago anual + soporte aparte</span>
      <span class="text-muted/40">·</span>
      <span class="text-muted/60 line-through">Software en la nube: cada mes, para siempre</span>
      <span class="text-muted/40">·</span>
      <span class="text-verde font-semibold">MI CAJA: una vez y listo</span>
    </div>

    <a
      href="https://wa.me/526141000000?text=Hola%2C%20me%20interesa%20MI%20CAJA%20punto%20de%20venta.%0AMi%20negocio%20es%3A%20%5Btipo%5D%0AMi%20nombre%20es%3A%20%5Bnombre%5D"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="inline-block bg-verde text-dark font-display font-bold text-base px-10 py-4 rounded-xl
             hover:glow-verde hover:-translate-y-0.5 active:translate-y-0
             transition-all duration-200"
    >
      Obtener MI CAJA — $3,000 →
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
